    "description": {
      "value": "<p>In order to use this maneuver, you must be within 5 feet of either a surface(Other than what you are standing on) or a creature a size.</p><p> When you would move you may roll a superiority die.</p><p> You bounce off the surface/creature, moving an amount of feet equal to the result of the die*5+10 in any direction.</p><p> If you run into another surface/creature you may move an additional 10 ft.</p><p> You can move up to 150 feet using this maneuver.</p><p></p>",
